title: Find New Music
description:
This is an idea, don&#039;t know if it&#039;s good but it might help some people. The idea is that I&#039;ve taken one or two songs from a lot of bands, songs that are representative for their style. Give the songs a listen and see if you find anything you like, then go out and buy their stuff. Sure, more than half of it won&#039;t fit you at all, but there could still be something in there, you know? So give it a shot.

DISCLAIMER: Some of these songs are old, some are 128kbps(but most of them are not). If you find anything you like, BUY THEIR STUFF! Thank you.
